Package: MAWEI
Title: Metro Atlanta Water-Energy Interdependencies (MAWEI)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hassan", "Niazi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hassan.niazi@pnnl.gov",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6556-2854"))
Description: Analyzes and visualizes water-energy interdependencies for the
    Metro Atlanta region using interactive Sankey diagrams. Provides data
    processing, aggregation, and plotting functions for energy and water flows.
